[10:15.27] [Retiring with HORATIO]
[10:17.01]LAERTES What ceremony else?
[10:30.18]HAMLET That is Laertes,
[10:31.60] A very noble youth: mark.
[10:33.09]LAERTES What ceremony else?
[10:35.29]First Priest Her obsequies have been as far enlarged
[10:38.19] As we have warrantise: her death was doubtful;
